const sqlJoiningOrdersCustomers = "To join order details with corresponding customer information, you use a simple inner join:\r\n\r\n```sql\r\nSELECT o.*, c.name, c.email\r\nFROM orders o\r\nJOIN customers c ON o.customer_id = c.id;\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis pulls all orders where a matching customer exists. If you need **every order**, even those without matching customers, switch to a LEFT JOIN:\r\n\r\n```sql\r\nSELECT o.*, c.name, c.email\r\nFROM orders o\r\nLEFT JOIN customers c ON o.customer_id = c.id;\r\n``` ";

